:: Grandma D1 [Quest]
time: time + 2
grandmaQ1: true
talkedGrandmaD1: true
--
She wants the photo of her grandchild recovered from a warped frame.

With careful hands you free it, whole. She presses your fingers in thanks.

*Grandma Quest 1 complete.*

Talking to her today closes the Garbage Scavenger's path — but opens Grandma's and the Local Artisan's.

[[Back to the shop->Shop]]


