:: Grandma D2 [Quest]
time: time + 2
grandmaQ2: true
talkedGrandmaD3: true
--
This time it is her own portrait, as a young woman.

You lift the silvering, steady the emulsion. She laughs at her younger face.

*Grandma Quest 2 complete.*

[[Back to the shop->Shop]]


:: Grandma Late [Quest]
time: time + 2
grandmaLate: true
talkedGrandmaD3: true
--
She came too late in the week for the full thread to be woven.

You recover one picture, and she thanks you — but the deeper story stays out of reach this loop.

*(Grandma & Local Artisan endings are out of reach this loop. The Garbage Scavenger's path stays open only if you keep your distance.)*

[[Back to the shop->Shop]]


