:: Grandma D3 [Quest]
time: time + 2
grandmaQ3: true
unlockedGrandmaEnding: true
--
The last photo: Grandma beside your grandpa, younger than you've ever seen him.

As you reseat the backing, a strip of paper slips free — a safe code, in your uncle's writing.

*Grandma Quest 3 complete. Grandma Ending unlocked — the safe will open now.*

[[Back to the shop->Shop]]


:: Artisan D3 [Quest]
time: time + 1
artisanQ3: true
--
You make the final piece look not new, but *true*. Lave nods — the hardest nod to earn.

*Local Artisan Quest 3 complete. You gain a delicate restoration tool and access to fragile objects.*

[[Back to the shop->Shop]]


:: Scavenger D3 [Quest]
time: time + 1
scavengerQ3: true
hasScavengerInfo: true
cash: cash + (Math.floor(Math.random() * (250 - 50 + 1)) + 50)
--
In the last crate, something genuinely old. He grins.

"You should meet Sam — a real archeologist. Tell him I sent you."

*Garbage Scavenger Quest 3 complete. You now carry a lead to the Local Archeologist (persists across loops).*

[[Back to the shop->Shop]]


:: Archeo D3 [Quest]
time: time + 1
archeoQ3: true
--
He unrolls a restored map and taps a mark.

"That is where your uncle's *final* fragment waits."

*Archeologist Quest 3 complete — the lead to the Final Uncle Artifact.*

[[Back to the shop->Shop]]


:: Buyer D5 [Artifact]
